Locations of each Pokemon:

ACE Pokemon will be added to your party.

Articuno: Outside Shoal Cave, speak to the sailor.
Zapdos: New Mauville, interact with item east of generator.
Moltres: Atop Mt. Chinmey, speak to the Lava Cookie Lady.

Pay Day Skitty: Mauville Game Corner, girl by the counter who gives you her spare plush.
Surfing Pichu: Route 127 Northwest item ball.

Wish Chansey: Speak to Prof. Cosmo in his house.

All other Pokemon: Lavaridge town Pokemon Center, speak to the youngster.

